additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Alcohol Denat., Water, Oil of Lemon Eucalyptus (hydrated, cyclized), Lemon Myrtle Oil (Backhousia citriodora).

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Not to be applied to infants under 12 months of age unless of doctor's advice. May cause allergy. Do not use if you have a known sensitivity to eucalyptus oil and/or natural fragrances. Do not take internally. Do not allow chemical containers or chemical to get into drains, sewers, streams or ponds. DO NOT spray towards face. DO NOT allow children to apply product to themselves. Shake well before use. Apply directly onto exposed skin. Reapply as necessary. NOT TO BE USED FOR ANY PURPOSE, OR IN ANY MANNER, CONTRARY TO THIS LABEL UNLESS AUTHORISED.
